'''甲基二氯化铋'''是一种[[有机铋化学|有机铋化合物]]，化学式为CH<sub>3</sub>BiCl<sub>2</sub>。它是浅黄色固体，可由二苯基甲基铋和[[氯化氢|氯化氢]]反应制得。它具有聚合结构，每个Bi中心由四个Cl<sup>−</sup>配体桥联。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1021/om000749i|title=Syntheses and Chemistry of Methylantimony and Methylbismuth Dihalides: An Extended Two-Dimensional Framework in the Crystal Structure of CH<sub>3</sub>BiCl<sub>2</sub> and Molecular Units in the Structures of [CH<sub>3</sub>ECl<sub>2</sub>(2,2'-bipyridine)] (E = Sb, Bi)|year=2001|last1=Althaus|first1=Henrik|last2=Breunig|first2=Hans Joachim|last3=Lork|first3=Enno|journal=Organometallics|volume=20|issue=3|pages=586–589}}</ref>它和二硫代芳基羧酸（ArCSSH）在[[三乙胺|三乙胺]]的存在下反应，可以得到二(二硫代芳基羧酸)甲基铋。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganica Chimica Acta|volume=363|issue=2|language=en|date=2010-01|pages=375–380|doi=10.1016/j.ica.2009.11.002|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0020169309006276|title=Monoorganobismuth(III) dithiocarboxylates: Synthesis, structures and their utility as molecular precursors for the preparation of Bi2S3 films and nanocrystals|accessdate=2020-12-15|author=Kamal R. Chaudhari, Neelam Yadav, Amey Wadawale, Vimal K. Jain, Rakesh Bohra|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819145401/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0020169309006276|dead-url=no}}</ref>

